    "description": "The hordes of chaos never stop, to survive the Warlocks War you need powerful skills and strategies. Warlock Survivors is the relentless battleground where you can face countless hordes of enemies in a single frantic run. The game is a Action Roguelite inspired in Vampire Survivors and Lord of the RIngs with different stages and enemies. You can increase your power and improve your skills by making the right decisions and face an army of thousands.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Combat Options</strong> - A frantic chaos on the battlefield, but not without options, to face the horde of enemies there are many possibilities, from varied special attacks to defense skills and support items.<br></li><li><strong>More Warlocks</strong> - The first character controlled is the Necromancer, but it is possible to unlock other warlocks by fulfilling certain objectives during the stages.<br></li><li><strong>Slow Motion</strong> - To enjoy the destruction even more, and also to take a breath, the slow motion skill can be acquired and improved.</li></ul>",
